videos.description: N'Faly Dante gathers the rock and throws it down to extend the Ducks' lead.
videos.headline: N'Faly Dante throws down the hammer for Oregon

videos.description: Quincy Guerrier snags the offensive board and muscles through his defender for the and-1.
videos.headline: Quincy Guerrier muscles through for an Oregon and-1

videos.description: Tristan da Silva dishes to Jabari Walker who throws it down with authority to pull the Buffaloes within three.

videos.description: KJ Simpson hits Keeshawn Barthelemy in stride as gets the and-1 to fall for the Buffaloes.

videos.description: Clear the runway as KJ Simpson takes flight and unloads a thunderous jam to extend the Buffaloes' lead.

videos.headline: KJ Simpson takes flight and throws it down for Colorado

videos.description: Tristan da Silva hauls in the nearly full-court dime from Luke O'Brien and slams it home to seal the victory over Oregon in the Pac-12 Quarterfinals.

videos.headline: Tristan da Silva throws it down to seal the victory for Colorado
